{
  "texts": [
    "To achieve this goal, designers must also consider the significant variability in human behavior.",
    "For instance, our data show a wide range of responses to the same prompt that resulted in different kinds of conversations and a varying number of design requirements, demonstrating high variability in human behavior.",
    "This challenge is further compounded by the chat conversation format's inherently unstructured and open-ended nature.",
    "Therefore, it is not just about \"herding AI cats\" but also about managing \"human cats.\"",
    "This metaphor underscores the need for designers to account for human behavior's unpredictability and LLMs' inherent unpredictability."
  ]
}